snippet.textDisplay: I appreciate that you are trying to do something new, when you already have a very successful formula. And the gear you're shooting with is absolutely to die for. But I'm sorry to say that I would never have subscribed to this ASMR POV channel. Your reactions to, and comments on the products, as well as your interactions with others in the studio (here's looking at you, Willy Du), are the main points that make your channel so interesting and fun. This is what makes Unbox Therapy not only a good tech channel, but also good entertainment. The amazement with the incredible autofocus does wear off quickly.
